metadata.name: Princess of Tomatoes
metadata.description:
There are some photos that are unforgettable for a lifetime. This photo is one of them. My mother and my little niece.

This photo I took in my own village has been my most shared photo on social media so far. Before I took this photo that made everyone smile, I was not aware that such a result would occur. I asked my niece to give me a tomato and she gave me a tomato in all its sweetness. I got a great photo.

The hue of the tomatoes and the sweetness of my niece really added a warm atmosphere to the photo. The photo of my mother in the background focusing on her own work really added a special value. Time will never stop, it will flow, but this photo will always live.

Camera: Nikon D5500
Lens: Nikkor 18-55 mm
Dimensions: 5000 × 3279
Resolution: 300 dpi
Location: Tokat, Turkey
Date: 28/07/2017
Edition: 1/1
